    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331530/extras/be32ffee2166c5ce01b831ab0219b8eb.poster.avif?t=1761577718\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331530/extras/be32ffee2166c5ce01b831ab0219b8eb.webm?t=1761577718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331530/extras/be32ffee2166c5ce01b831ab0219b8eb.mp4?t=1761577718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>扬帆并开始在一个神秘的海盗岛上的惊险冒险。深入一个开放世界的生存工艺游戏，其中每个角落都充满了危险和奇迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331530/extras/8a4de09384988f64e710cf15f73ddde8.avif?t=1761577718\" width=600 height=290 /></span>航行于危险的水域，探索隐藏的海湾，并揭示岛屿的秘密。海盗岛的每一寸都充满了等待被发现的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存和制作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从船只残骸中回收材料，收集资源，并制作必要的工具和武器。建造自己的海盗避难所对抗自然元素和更多的事物至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331530/extras/fishing.png?t=1761577718\" /></span>周围的水域充满了异国的海洋生物。投下钓线并为生存而钓鱼，或潜入波浪之下以遇见深海的神秘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331530/extras/brewing.png?t=1761577718\" /></span>朗姆酒不仅仅是为了庆祝！酿造强烈的饮料以保持士气高昂并保持船员的忠诚。但请记住，在这些危险的时期，节制是关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏的秘密</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但请注意，这个岛不仅仅是关于生存和宝藏。它拥有像海洋一样深邃和广阔的秘密。你有勇气揭示它们吗？</p>",
